body_html: FYI, the number of the exported symbols in caffe2.dll is 16938, while it increased to 51473 for caffe2_gpu.dll with CUDA 9. The number of that in caffe2.dll built with VS 2015 is 19444. The caffe2_gpu.dll could not be generated so I cannot get the exact number.

body: FYI, the number of the exported symbols in `caffe2.dll` is 16938, while it increased to 51473 for `caffe2_gpu.dll` with CUDA 9. The number of that in `caffe2.dll` built with VS 2015 is 19444. The `caffe2_gpu.dll` could not be generated so I cannot get the exact number.
